description:
The Losers hop on the turtle for the sixth episode revolving around Stephen King's 1986 epic. Together, they close the book for good by wading through the sewers of "Part 5: The Ritual of Chüd" and "Derry: The Last Interlude". 


Chapters include: Introduction, Heroes and Villains (5:25), The Ritual of Bëv. (1:37:00), Heroes and Villains Continued (1:50:00), Misery (2:09:00), The Sematary (2:17:30), Word Processor of the Gods (2:29:00), Poundcake (2:39:30), King's Dominion (2:44:00), Final Thoughts (2:49:40), and Outro (3:02:00).
